returns._0: Whether or not the execution succeeded

params._functionBytecodes: RLP-Encoded parameters for executions of the agenda
params._targets: Target addresses for executions of the agenda

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

params._minimumNoticePeriodSeconds: New minimum notice period in seconds

params._minimumVotingPeriodSeconds: New minimum voting period in seconds

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

endAgendaVoting(uint256).notice: Set the agenda status as ended(denied or dismissed)

setCreateAgendaFees(uint256).notice: Set the fee(TON) of creating an agenda

setExecutedAgenda(uint256).notice: Set the agenda status as executed

setExecutingPeriodSeconds(uint256).notice: Set the executing period in seconds

setMinimumNoticePeriodSeconds(uint256).notice: Set the minimum notice period in seconds

setMinimumVotingPeriodSeconds(uint256).notice: Set the minimum voting period in seconds
